  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Third Wild</h2>Third wild is a survival game with a variety of gameplay, That will make you enjoy the adventure of fighting monsters. You will be playing the role of The man who woke up in a foreign land explore and survive in the unknown land Build relationships, trade things, go on adventures and build your own home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features :</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hunting.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/6efcceea3853717c174f9b019c32d966.poster.avif?t=1664371767\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/6efcceea3853717c174f9b019c32d966.webm?t=1664371767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/6efcceea3853717c174f9b019c32d966.mp4?t=1664371767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cooking.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/f5130b453b3778026f852bd97ab6a874.poster.avif?t=1664371767\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/f5130b453b3778026f852bd97ab6a874.webm?t=1664371767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074040/extras/f5130b453b3778026f852bd97ab6a874.mp4?t=1664371767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Skill tree.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app